address.streetAddress: Jordan Plan, Terrace at Riverview Landing

location.fullValue: Jordan Plan, Terrace at Riverview Landing

data.description: Wonderful 2-story Craftsman home on a full basement in the desirable Enclave at Oakdale neighborhood! Enjoy coming home to an open-concept layout from the kitchen to living room that is perfect for daily family time and the occasional entertaining. Lots of newer improvements added including: Fresh new interior paint, luxury vinyl floors throughout, all newer windows bringing in fabulous natural light, a whole home water softener and reverse osmosis water spicket in kitchen, plus more (the owner's improvements list is available). The large kitchen has all stainless steel appliances, plenty of cabinet storage, a breakfast bar and dining area. Step right out to a new deck with an included gazebo overlooking the fenced backyard. All 4 bedrooms are upstairs including the laundry room, the master suite with 2 walk-in closets, master bathroom with separate vanities, a separate tub and shower. 3 additional bedrooms share a full bathroom with a double vanity. A 12 bathroom and cozy office nook are also featured on the main level. The unfinished basement is prepped to finish (has newer electrical, air ducts, and stubbed for a full bathroom) with access right out to a screened in patio! Don't miss the neighborhood swimming pool and your dedicated walking trail to Riverview Landing to enjoy restaurants, retail, a brewery, more! Super convenient location with easy access to I-285, I-20, Vinings, Hartsfield airport, and downtown Atlanta.
